# Images Directory

This directory contains images for the portfolio including:

- Hero images for projects
- Profile photos
- Screenshots and mockups
- OpenGraph images
- Favicons and icons

## Recommended Structure

```
images/
├── hero/
│   ├── project-name-hero.jpg
│   └── ...
├── screenshots/
│   ├── project-name-1.png
│   └── ...
├── profile/
│   ├── profile-photo.jpg
│   └── ...
└── og/
    ├── og-image.jpg
    ├── project-name-og.jpg
    └── ...
```

## Image Optimization

- Use WebP format when possible
- Keep hero images under 200KB
- Use responsive images with Next.js Image component
- Provide alt text for accessibility

## Required Images

- og-image.jpg (1200x630 for OpenGraph)
- favicon.ico
- apple-touch-icon.png (180x180)
- android-chrome-192x192.png
- android-chrome-512x512.png
